msgstr ""
"指定要匹配的單個 UID 或 UID 範圍，例如 1000 以匹配相應的 UID 或 1000-1005 以"
"包含匹配相應範圍內的所有 UID"

msgid ""
"Specifies that duplicate frames (received on inactive ports) should be "
