"Specifies the wired ports to attach to this bridge. In order to attach "
"wireless networks, choose the associated interface as network in the "
"wireless settings."
msgstr ""
"指定要附加到該橋接的有線連接埠。為了連接無線網路，請在無線設定中選擇關聯的介"
